summary: Sometimes, I wonder what happened to my first Pokemon Red cartridge.  I do have Pokemon Red, somewhere, but it isn’t the one I...
body:
Sometimes, I wonder what happened to my first Pokemon Red cartridge. 

I do have Pokemon Red, somewhere, but it isn’t the one I started with. My mom had found it in the parking lot of the place she worked at at the time, and gave it to me to see if it worked. (By the way, it still does.)

But neither my mom nor I know what happened to my first Red cartridge, or the Blue one that my dad used to have that I later took over.
